    "actor": "https://uofa.net/morrison/actor/credibility-assessment-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are formally not-assessed, which is acceptable under ASME V&V 40 at MRL 2. The predicted relative hemolysis index remains below 1.0 at all five operating points, satisfying the acceptance criterion. The assessment team concludes that the CFD model provides sufficient credibility to support the worst-case hemolysis operating condition determination for this Class II CPB device.",
